headline: How PepsiCo, Cadence Bank, And Skyworks Solutions Can Put Cash In Your Pocket
summary: Companies with a long history of paying dividends and consistently hiking them remain appealing to income-focused investors. PepsiCo, Cadence Bank, and Skyworks Solutions have rewarded shareholders for years and recently announced dividend increases. ...
